'''Ciryandil''' or '''Kiryandil''' can refer to:

*[[Ciryandil]], the fourteenth [[King of Gondor]].
*[[Kiryandil (son of Siriondil)|Kiryandil]], the father of King [[Eärnil II]], according to an abandoned draft of the ''[[Appendices]]''.
*[[Elendur (son of Isildur)|Kiryandil]], an early version of Elendur, the eldest son of [[Isildur]], according to an abandoned draft of the ''Appendices''.
